<br>
1) We could establish a network of spies, maybe members of other guilds (probably a very risky idea but consider the payoff: information after all is the strongest weapon) and use this information for sabotage, blackmail, etc. (if its at all possible to implement on EQ).<br>
<br>
2) As mentioned in previous messages we could be used for hire (assassinations, scouting, escort, illegal trade)<br>
